    "Further examples will be considered in Sect.",
    "\"The need for trustworthy AI, and XAI in particular\".",
    "Many bias mitigation techniques assume in input the specification of one or more protected attributes to mitigate the bias against.",
    "However, different dimensions of identity cannot be understood in isolation but must be considered collectively to grasp the full complexity of individuals.",
    "A special effort must hence be employed to consider the interplay of the different (protected) attributes (Ovalle et al., 2023)."
